#Text= Gun says : " Sadly , most of your servants were scattered and the royal things were looted after the queen was removed from office .

column1: #Text=So your coronation may not have some of the usual items ... like ... the crown .
#Text=How can you have a coronation without a crown ?
#Text=How will people know when I 'm officially the king ?
#Text=" Gun says : " We still have one of the royal jewels we can pin on you .
#Text=" Gun says : " Think of it more as a royal brooch .
#Text=" Wu says : " Are you telling me that there are no dancing badgermoles ?
#Text=No acrobat bell ringers , no horn blowing announcery guy ?
#Text=" Gun says : " It will be a very simple , intimate , elegant ceremony .
#Text=Just try on the brooch , Your Grace , you will see it looks beautiful ... " Wu says : " Do n't ... touch me .
